casebody.data:
Brenda ELEM, et al., petitioners,
v.
AIRTRAN AIRWAYS, INC. No. 14-1061. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 25, 2016.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit. Petition for certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit for further consideration in light of Montanile v. Board of Trustees of Nat. Elevator Industry Health Benefit Plan, 577 U.S. ----, 136 S.Ct. 651, --- L.Ed.2d ---- (2016).
